Known issues in ResidualVM 0.3.0git:

Common
------
 * Switching full-screen/windowed with alt-enter might crash ResidualVM
 * Running fullscreen in widescreen monitors might stretch the image
   You can try solve issue by using config file option: "fullscreen_res".
   See README.md file for more information.

Grim
----
 * Characters might pop into place at times
 * Some animations will show their initial state at the end

MYST III
--------
 * Catherine's extra speech at start is distorted, see issue #1038
